p.font: Docker Engine is a client-server application with these major components:

li.font: A server which is a type of long-running program called a daemon process (thedockerd command).
A REST API which specifies interfaces that programs can use to talk to the
daemon and instruct it what to do.

font.font: A command line interface (CLI) client (the docker command).
